race.comment: FLYWHEEL (1) has hit a purple patch of form of late with two wins and a second from his past three starts and is racing high on confidence. Perfectly placed here and can continue on the upward trajectory. Former Victorian CAPITAL ASSET (7) is having his first run for the new barn but should find this easier than what he faced down south. Respect any push in betting. NIGHTSTICK (13) is yet to miss a drum in four starts at this track and maps ideally from gate two. Include in calculations. CHINCHILLA AHEAD (11) drops back in grade after a midfield effort in Class 6 company last start. Much better suited at this level and won well at Toowoomba two back.
